Jason Derulo is set to become a dad after announcing that he’s expecting his first child with girlfriend Jena Frumes. The Ridin’ Solo singer shared the news of Jena’s pregnancy with a sweet video announcement filmed during their holiday in the Bahamas. ‘Couldn’t be more excited for this new chapter in our life,’ Jason captioned the post while Jena shared a photo of them together, calling each other ‘mom and dad’. See video HERE